Those of you who have foreign friends and connections, please help us share this: The Special Envoy Office of the United Nations Global Covid-19 Humanitarian Response Plan and the Jack Ma Foundation have invited a number of first-line physicians who participated in the treatment of the new coronaviruses. It took them three weeks to write a manual for hospitals, doctors and nurses, and it finally came online today. The vast majority of hospitals around the world will face these challenges, and we particularly hope to share these experiences with hospitals and healthcare providers around the world as soon as possible, So please help download, print, or forward it to your local hospitals and/or healthcare providers so they can be fully prepared. Thank you!
① Handbook of COVID-19 Prevention and Treatment: https://covid-19.alibabacloud.com/zh
Handbook Chinese version: https://www.alibabacloud.com/zh/universal-service/pdf_reader? pdf=Handbook_of_COVID 19 Prevention_zh_Moblie.pdf
③ Handbook English version: https://www.alibabacloud.com/zh/universal-service/pdf_reader? pdf=Handbook_of_COVID 19 Prevention_en_Mobile.pdf
Wish you all the best!
